{"id":4016,"date":"2021-11-10T09:21:00","date_gmt":"2021-11-10T08:21:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/?p=4016"},"modified":"2022-05-09T16:55:46","modified_gmt":"2022-05-09T15:55:46","slug":"mirissa","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/mirissa\/","title":{"rendered":"9 Great Things To Do in Mirissa, Sri Lanka"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"todo\">1. Secret Beach, Mirissa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Secret Beach might not be a secret anymore, but it still feels like a remote island paradise! The small, secluded beach is tucked around the corner from the main beach in Mirissa and is a little harder to get to. Because of this, fewer people visit the beach, and if you get there early enough, you can even have the whole place to yourself! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-sunset.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6869 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155119\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-sunset.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155119\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-sunset-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155119\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-sunset-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155119\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-sunset-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155119\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-sunset-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155119\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-sunset-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155119\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-sunset-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155119\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-sunset-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155119\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-sunset-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155119\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-sunset-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155119\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-sunset-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155119\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-sunset-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155119\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-sunset-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155119\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-sunset-24x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155119\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-sunset.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>There are 3 beautiful beaches to choose from on this headland, each with its own unique characteristics, from rockpools to coconut palm trees. Spend the day enjoying the crystal blue water, snorkeling among incredible marine life (make sure to keep your eyes peeled for turtles!), and enjoying every moment of this slice of heaven.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> There&#x2019;s no entry fee to visit the beaches, but please buy some food, drinks, sunbeds, or snorkels from the locals working here to support the economy. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>To get there, search <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/tmWhaBdzwW92\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Google Maps<\/a> for Secret Beach bar and ask a tuk-tuk driver to take you there. You will need to walk 10 minutes from the drop-off point as the road is too steep for tuk-tuks.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6870 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-24x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"parrot\">2. Parrot Rock<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Parrot Rock sits directly In front of Mirissa Beach: a huge red-colored mound that towers over the water. It&#x2019;s become one of the best things to do in Mirissa as it has beautiful views of the palm tree-lined beaches below. <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Because Parrot Rock sits out at sea, you&#x2019;ll have to research the tides as low tide is the safest time to cross over (and you&#x2019;ll avoid getting wet). It can be dangerous to cross over during high tide, especially in the monsoon season when the waves will be high.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-parrot-rock.jpg\" alt=\"Things To Do Mirissa Sri Lanka parrot rock\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"303\" alt=\"Things To Do Mirissa Sri Lanka parrot rock\" class=\"wp-image-6889 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155047\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-parrot-rock.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155047\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-parrot-rock-300x202.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155047\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-parrot-rock-600x404.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155047\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-parrot-rock-450x303.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155047\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-parrot-rock-800x539.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155047\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-parrot-rock-1080x728.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155047\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-parrot-rock-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155047\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-parrot-rock-163x110.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155047\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-parrot-rock-267x180.jpg 267w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155047\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-parrot-rock-768x518.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155047\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-parrot-rock-1024x690.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155047\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-parrot-rock-1440x971.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155047\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-parrot-rock-30x20.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155047\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-parrot-rock.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Once you reach the rock, climb the rickety stairs to the top. From here, you&#x2019;ll see beautiful views across Mirissa. It&#x2019;s particularly popular to visit at sunset but can get very crowded. Because of this, we recommend getting up early and climbing at sunrise. At this time, you can see the beautiful early morning pinks and oranges of the Mirissa skyline, and watch the light filter through the green palm trees.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Find all:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/mirissa-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Hotels in Mirissa<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"coconut\">3. Coconut Tree Hill: Top Things to do Mirissa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Coconut Tree Hill is one of the most Instagrammable spots in Sri Lanka and one of the top things to do in Mirissa. The private coconut farm is just a 15-minute walk from Mirissa Beach and offers some of the best views in the area! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114028\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-spot-2.jpg\" alt=\"Things To Do mirissa Sri Lanka coconut tree spot\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Things To Do mirissa Sri Lanka coconut tree spot\" class=\"wp-image-34259 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114028\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-spot-2.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114028\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-spot-2-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114028\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-spot-2-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltin