a-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114028\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-spot-2.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Once you reach the top of the hill, the headland stretches out ahead of you, allowing you spectacular views over the ocean through the many leaning palm trees. We recommend going at sunrise to take photos when there are fewer people around.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-photography-tips\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Travel photography tips &amp; tricks<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14124327\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-photo-spot.jpg\" alt=\"mirissa sri lanka things to do\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"mirissa sri lanka things to do\" class=\"wp-image-68948 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14124327\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-photo-spot.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14124327\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-photo-spot-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/