=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/14124327\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-photo-spot.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>You can find the location of Coconut Tree Hill on <a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.nl\/maps\/place\/Palm+Tree+Hill+-+Wonderful+View\/@5.9396793,80.4680048,17.75z\/data=!4m13!1m7!3m6!1s0x3ae13fce3177dc59:0xa2d8a78b36dc9c90!2sMirissa,+Sri+Lanka!3b1!8m2!3d5.948262!4d80.4715866!3m4!1s0x3ae13e324bc0846b:0x35758cdcba8dedcf!8m2!3d5.9393076!4d80.4685436\">Google Maps<\/a>. If the weather is good and the tide is low, you can walk along the beach. Be aware that at certain times you may need to walk through water. If not, you can walk along the road that hugs the coastline.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> True to its name, there are coconuts in the trees at Coconut Hill. Be careful, as they can fall, so never stand directly under the trees.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--visa \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--visa\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/get-visa-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">Order your Sri Lanka Visa online<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4016&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155059\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-pin.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155059\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-pin-20x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155059\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-pin-407x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"9 Great Things To Do in Mirissa, Sri Lanka\" height=\"600\" width=\"407\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"4-weligama\">4. Weligama<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Weligama is a small beach town that&#x2019;s widely known as the capital of surfing. Surfers flock here from all over the world to enjoy the fantastic waves and beautiful white-sand beaches. Because of this, there&#x2019;s also excellent tourism infrastructure, with plenty of trendy bars, cafes, restaurants, and beach resorts.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23