und-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Getting there:<\/strong> Mirissa to Weligama is only a 15-minute drive. Simply rent a motorbike or pay for a tuk-tuk to drive you there.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111116\/weligama-sri-lanka.jpg\" alt=\"weligama sri lanka\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"329\" alt=\"weligama sri lanka\" class=\"wp-image-43974 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111116\/weligama-sri-lanka.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111116\/weligama-sri-lanka-300x219.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111116\/weligama-sri-lanka-600x438.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111116\/weligama-sri-lanka-800x584.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111116\/weligama-sri-lanka-1080x789.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111116\/weligama-sri-lanka-450x329.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111116\/weligama-sri-lanka-1536x1122.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111116\/weligama-sri-lanka-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111116\/weligama-sri-lanka-163x119.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111116\/weligama-sri-lanka-247x180.jpg 247w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111116\/weligama-sri-lanka-768x561.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/