ka\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\" content=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23152400\/Thumb-Thebeautyof-SriLanka-800x450.jpg\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"uploadDate\" content=\"2018-07-02 16:06:57\">\n\n\n                <div class=\"video-block video-block--mediavine\">\n                    <div class=\"video-block__embed\">\n                        <div class=\"mv-video-target mv-video-id-d9dlr5yjewfgvdxeqruh\" data-video-id=\"d9dlr5yjewfgvdxeqruh\" data-volume=\"70\" data-ratio=\"16:9\" data-autoinsert=\"true\" data-disable-jsonld=\"true\"><\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <a class=\"video-block__credit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/c\/saltinourhair?sub_confirmation=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"YouTube Salt in our Hair\">\n                    <div class=\"socials__item\">\n                        <span class=\"socials__link\">\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-youtube\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-youtube\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <span>Subscribe to our <b>YouTube channel<\/b> and never miss a video!<\/span>\n                <\/a>\n\n                <div class=\"video-block__bg\">\n                    <img class=\"video-block__bg-image lazyload\" data-src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23152400\/Thumb-Thebeautyof-SriLanka-800x450.jpg\" alt=\"Sri Lanka\" height=\"450\" width=\"800\">\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Please research your tour carefully and make sure the company you are using respects international whale watching rules, and works to protect these beautiful creatures. Sustainable and ethical companies will be passionate about conservation and never allow the boat to get too close to the whales.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Not planning a visit in that season? In the opposite season, it is one of the popular <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/trincomalee\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">things to do in Trincomalee<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n\n    <a class=\"ebook-banner ebook-banner--sl\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/shop\/ebooks\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n        <img src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" data-src=\"\/build\/images\/ebooks\/traveling-sri-lanka\/slebook-banner.jpg\" class=\"lazypreload\" height=\"225\" width=\"800\" alt=\"Ebook Sri Lanka\">\n    <\/a>\n    \n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"galle\">6. Unawatuna &amp; Galle Fort Day Trip<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Unawatuna is one of the most popular beach towns on the south coast of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a>. It&#x2019;s famous for its sandy beaches, hipster restaurants, and lively nightlife. As it&#x2019;s only a short 50-minute drive from Mirissa, it&#x2019;s the perfect place to visit on a day trip.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hire a motorbike and drive along the coastline to spend the morning in Unawatuna. Swim at the beaches, enjoy the famous Dalawella beach swing, or snap some photos of the ocean views from the Japanese Peace Pagoda. It&#x2019;s also a great place to hire a board and learn to surf, as it&#x2019;s known for its beginner-sized waves.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/unawatuna\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Unmissable things to do in Unawatuna!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach.jpg\" alt=\"things to do unawatuna sri lanka beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"305\" alt=\"things to do unawatuna sri lanka beach\" class=\"wp-image-7371 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-300x203.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-600x406.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-450x305.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-800x542.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-1080x731.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-163x110.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-266x180.jpg 266w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-768x520.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-1024x693.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-1440x975.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-30x20.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"galle-fort\"><strong>Galle Fort<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Galle Fort is a 15-minute drive from Unawatuna and a must-see on your day trip! The ancient fort town is a melting pot of culture, having survived the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Portuguese<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/netherlands\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Dutch<\/a> and British invasions. It&#x2019;s the perfect place to spend the afternoon, shopping at the cute boutique shops and admiring the charming, traditional buildings. Make sure to watch the sunset from the Galle Fort wall &#x2013; the perfect way to end the day!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read more:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/galle-fort\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Galle Fort, a trip back in history<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-gall-fort.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6882 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155054\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-gall-fort.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155054\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-gall-fort-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155054\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-gall-fort-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155054\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-gall-fort-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155054\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-gall-fort-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155054\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-gal