e advantage of the delicious food at one of the many beachside restaurants and cafes!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121055\/best-surf-sri-lanka.jpg\" alt=\"best surf sri lanka\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"319\" alt=\"best surf sri lanka\" class=\"wp-image-22456 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121055\/best-surf-sri-lanka.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121055\/best-surf-sri-lanka-300x213.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121055\/best-surf-sri-lanka-600x425.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121055\/best-surf-sri-lanka-800x567.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121055\/best-surf-sri-lanka-1080x766.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121055\/best-surf-sri-lanka-450x319.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121055\/best-surf-sri-lanka-1536x1089.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121055\/best-surf-sri-lanka-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121055\/best-surf-sri-lanka-163x116.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121055\/best-surf-sri-lanka-254x180.jpg 254w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121055\/best-surf-sri-lanka-768x544.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121055\/best-surf-sri-lanka-1024x726.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121055\/best-surf-sri-lanka-1440x1021.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121055\/best-surf-sri-lanka-30x21.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121055\/best-surf-sri-lanka.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"beach\">8. Mirissa Beach<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mirissa Beach is also exceptionally popular for holidaymakers who are simply looking to relax and swim. Although it can get crowded, the sandy bay sandwiched between coconut palms and rocky headland is still very peaceful. It&#x2019;s also not super busy with surf schools, unlike some other locations on the southern coast, so it&#x2019;s easy to enjoy a refreshing dip.&#xA0;&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>A handful of excellent restaurants are located on the edge of the beach, all offering different kinds of foods. Spending an afternoon here soaking up the chilled <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lankan <\/a>way of life is a top thing to do in Mirissa.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-beach.jpg\" alt=\"Things To Do Mirissa Sri Lanka beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"324\" alt=\"Things To Do Mirissa Sri Lanka beach\" class=\"wp-image-6895 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.sa