om\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155031\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-beach.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"9-matara\">9. Matara<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Experience real <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lankan<\/a> local life in Matara. The busy commercial town is not known as a vacation destination so there&#x2019;s very little tourism. Because of this, the town is a true representation of beautiful Sri Lankan culture. Wander the streets, doing as the locals do: hanging around on the peaceful, sandy beach or playing sports inside Matara Fort.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>To get to Matara, follow the coastline east from Mirissa by motorbike or tuk-tuk. The journey takes 30-minutes.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111128\/mirissa-things-to-do-matara-sri-lanka-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"mirissa things to do matara sri lanka\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"mirissa things to do matara sri lanka\" class=\"wp-image-43970 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111128\/mirissa-things-to-