-sri-lanka-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111135\/matara-sri-lanka-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111135\/matara-sri-lanka-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111135\/matara-sri-lanka-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111135\/matara-sri-lanka-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111135\/matara-sri-lanka-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111135\/matara-sri-lanka-1440x961.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111135\/matara-sri-lanka.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111135\/matara-sri-lanka-30x20.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23111135\/matara-sri-lanka-1080x721.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>One of the top things to see in Matara is the stunning Paravi Duwa Temple. This traditional Buddhist temple sits on an island surrounded by the beautiful blue Indian Ocean. Most unique of all is that the temple is connected to the town by a steel bridge. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Tip<\/strong>: Remember to cover your head, arms, and legs as a sign of respect, as this is a sacred place of worship for the local people.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"doctors-house-matara\">Doctors House (Matara)<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready for a great afternoon party with surf vibes? The Doctors House is the place to visit! The extensive garden has the perfect laid-back vibe, great food, drinks, and live music. Plus, it&#x2019;s only a short 15-minute drive out of Matara.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-doctors-house-restaurant.jpg\" alt=\"Things To Do Mirissa Sri Lanka doctors house restaurant\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"316\" alt=\"Things To Do Mirissa Sri Lanka doctors house restaurant\" class=\"wp-image-6875 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155104\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-doctors-house-restaurant.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155104\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-doctors-house-restaurant-300x211.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155104\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-doctors-house-restaurant-600x422.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155104\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-doctors-house-restaurant-450x316.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155104\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-doctors-house-restaurant-800x563.jpg 800w, https